<li class="leading-relaxed"><a href="../adversaries/Assassin%20Poisoner.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Assassin Poisoner</a></li>
<li class="leading-relaxed"><a href="../adversaries/Master%20Assassin.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Master Assassin</a></li>
